---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Services — Nellie Borrero" description="Professional speaking services, strategic advisory, and transformative keynotes on leadership excellence and organizational culture." path="/services">
	<!-- Services Section -->
	<section class="container py-12">
		<h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-plum">Services</h1>
		<p class="mt-3 max-w-prose text-lg">Bring Nellie to your audience</p>
		
		<!-- Service Cards -->
		<div class="mt-12 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
			<article class="rounded-lg border border-gray-200 p-6 bg-white">
				<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-plum mb-4">Global Speaking</h2>
				<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">Transformative keynotes and presentations for corporations, conferences, and educational institutions. Engaging, story-driven content focused on leadership excellence and organizational performance.</p>
			</article>

			<article class="rounded-lg border border-gray-200 p-6 bg-white">
				<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-plum mb-4">Strategic Advisory</h2>
				<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">Executive guidance on leadership strategy, organizational transformation, and performance accountability. Based on proven experience leading global organizational change.</p>
			</article>

			<article class="rounded-lg border border-gray-200 p-6 bg-white">
				<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-plum mb-4">Media Commentary</h2>
				<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">Expert insights and thought leadership on leadership, workplace culture, and organizational effectiveness for media outlets, podcasts, and industry publications.</p>
			</article>
		</div>

		<!-- Target Audiences and Categories -->
		<div class="mt-16 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2">
			<div class="rounded-lg border border-gray-200 p-6 bg-white">
				<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-plum mb-4">Who We Serve</h3>
				<ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
					<li>• Corporations, non-profits and educational institutions seeking leadership excellence</li>
					<li>• CEOs, C-suite executives, and board members</li>
					<li>• Human Resources and Leadership Development executives</li>
					<li>• Executive teams and people managers</li>
					<li>• Professionals seeking high-performing, merit-based organizations</li>
					<li>• Students and emerging leaders</li>
				</ul>
			</div>

			<div class="rounded-lg border border-gray-200 p-6 bg-white">
				<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-plum mb-4">Expertise Areas</h3>
				<ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
					<li>• Leadership and executive development</li>
					<li>• Corporate culture and organizational excellence</li>
					<li>• Talent management and career development</li>
					<li>• Workforce dynamics: engagement, teamwork, and performance</li>
					<li>• Organizational effectiveness and business strategy</li>
					<li>• Employee resource strategy and business alignment</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Keynotes Section -->
	<section class="bg-gray-50 py-16">
		<div class="container">
			<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-plum text-center mb-4">Keynote Topics</h2>
			<p class="text-center text-gray-600 mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Transformative speaking engagements that inspire leadership excellence and drive organizational performance</p>
			
			<!-- Keynote Topics -->
			<div class="space-y-8">
				<article class="rounded-lg border border-gray-200 p-8 bg-white">
					<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-plum mb-4">Developing Emerging Leaders</h3>
					<h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">How leaders can accelerate talent development</h4>
					<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">What does it mean to truly lead and develop high-potential employees within organizations? In her book Unwavering, Nellie Borrero shows leaders how to ensure equal opportunities for every employee and guide individuals throughout their career journeys based on merit and potential.</p>
				</article>

				<article class="rounded-lg border border-gray-200 p-8 bg-white">
					<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-plum mb-4">Building High-Performance Culture</h3>
					<h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">Sustaining excellence in organizational DNA</h4>
					<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">Leaders often struggle to sustain cultural progress when they face new challenges or disruptions. Nellie offers a roadmap for leaders based on her own experience building and nurturing a culture of excellence and empowerment through lasting initiatives.</p>
				</article>

				<article class="rounded-lg border border-gray-200 p-8 bg-white">
					<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-plum mb-4">Authentic Leadership Development</h3>
					<h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">Become an advocate for your professional growth</h4>
					<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">Confidently stepping into your leadership potential and maintaining your authentic professional identity can be challenging for emerging leaders. Through her personal story in Unwavering, Nellie shows that authentic leadership drives both individual and organizational success.</p>
				</article>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Contact Section -->
	<section class="container py-12">
		<div class="text-center">
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-plum mb-4">Ready to Transform Your Organization?</h2>
			<p class="text-gray-600 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Book Nellie for your next event, strategic initiative, or organizational transformation.</p>
			<a class="btn-primary text-lg px-8 py-4" href="mailto:contact@nellieborrero.com">Contact Nellie Borrero</a>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>

